query:
SELECT structure_id AS structure_id,
       jurisdiction_id AS jurisdiction_id,
       task_id AS task_id,
       plan_id AS plan_id,
       geojson AS geojson
FROM
  (SELECT structure_id,
          structure_jurisdiction_id as jurisdiction_id,
          task_id,
          plan_id,
          jsonb_build_object('type', 'Feature', 'id', structure_id, 'geometry', ST_AsGeoJSON(structure_geometry)::jsonb, 'properties', to_jsonb(row) - 'structure_id' - 'structure_geometry') AS geojson
   FROM
     (SELECT structure_id,
             structure_jurisdiction_id,
             structure_code,
             structure_name,
             structure_type,
             structure_geometry,
             task_id,
             plan_id,
             event_date,
             business_status,
             rooms_eligible,
             rooms_sprayed,
             eligibility,
             structure_sprayed,
             business_status
      FROM zambia_irs_structures) row) AS expr_qry
WHERE jurisdiction_id = '92a0c5f3-8b47-465e-961b-2998ad3f00a5'
LIMIT 3000;
